beginning, containing an area of TEN THOUSAND SEVEN HUNDRED NINETY NINE (10,799) SQUARE METERS , more or less.

The parcel of land reserved herein for housing site purposes and declared open for disposition shall be disposed of under the provisions of Republic Act No. 730 in relation to the provisions of Commonwealth Act No. 141, otherwise known as the Public Land Act. The same shall be subject to private rights, if there be any, road right of way requirements, and to actual survey.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila this 9 th day of March, in the year of Our Lord, two thousand and four.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

